CANONICAL FOLDER STRUCTURE

This repository follows a staged, phase-based structure and this document
serves as the normative directory guide.

Root
│
├── README.md
├── FREEZE.md
├── FORKING_RULES.md
├── LICENSE
├── LICENSE_CONTEXT.md
├── STRUCTURE.md
│
├── 00_CONTEXT/
│   ├── project_intent.md
│   ├── scope_and_limits.md
│   └── regulatory_notes_mauritius.md
│
├── 01_STAGE_FOUNDATION/
│   ├── assumptions_and_constraints.md
│   ├── safety_principles.md
│   └── tools_and_skill_baseline.md
│
├── 02_STAGE_MECHANICAL/
│   ├── frame_analysis.md
│   ├── frame_reinforcement_concept.md
│   ├── motor_mounting.md
│   └── torque_and_fasteners.md
│
├── 03_STAGE_ELECTRICAL/
│   ├── system_architecture.md
│   ├── controller_canonical_profile.md
│   ├── wiring_and_protection.md
│   └── dc_dc_and_auxiliary.md
│
├── 04_STAGE_BATTERY/
